<section id="about" class="box">
  <h2 class="gradient-text">About Me</h2>
  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>Hello! I'm a DevOps enthusiast currently pursuing my career in the field of cloud and automation. I'm excited to share that I'm currently working as a DevOps Intern at Bootcoding Pvt. Ltd in Nagpur, where I'm gaining hands-on experience with industry-standard tools and practices.</p>
      <p>As a fresher in the DevOps field, I'm passionate about learning and implementing modern DevOps practices, with a particular focus on:</p>
      <ul class="focus-areas">
        <li><i class="ph-cloud-bold"></i> Cloud Infrastructure</li>
        <li><i class="ph-git-branch-bold"></i> CI/CD Pipelines</li>
        <li><i class="ph-cube-bold"></i> Containerization</li>
        <li><i class="ph-terminal-window-bold"></i> Automation</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="internship-highlight">
        <h3>Current Role</h3>
        <div class="role-details">
          <span class="company gradient-text">Bootcoding Pvt. Ltd</span>
          <span class="position">DevOps Intern</span>
          <span class="location">Nagpur, India</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 3rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  p {
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .focus-areas {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .focus-areas li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: #4b5563;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .focus-areas i {
    color: var(--gradient-start);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .internship-highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff10 0%, #bc52ee10 100%);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .internship-highlight h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .role-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .company {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .position {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #4b5563;
  }

  .location {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .about-content {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .focus-areas {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>